<description>Multiple XSAM Listen Ports (Incoming Channels) and Single Outgoing Channel		
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Step1: Provisioned Multiple XSAM Listen Ports (Incoming Channels) for CP.
Step2: Provisioned Single Outgoing Channel  in XSAM.
Step3: Simulate multiple CP Using XTT Client Simulator connecting to XSAM on different Port
Step4: Simulate SMSC for same Outgoing channel (Live Simulator)
Step5: Create Multiple SMPP Proxy Service for same Outgoing Channel. SMS Proxy Services created for this test should be active. 
Step6: Send a  "bind_transceiver" PDU from each CP Simulator to SMSC.
Step7: SMSC sends back the ACK to CP Simulator
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
</description>

